title: Cafe SOK
description: English menu is available. Vegan and raw food choices, and some vegetarian dishes can be made vegan. Free Wi-Fi. Have also delivery service. Plenty of vegan and raw food choices in extensive menu. Has an outdoor veranda, 2 non-smoking rooms inside. Located opposite Tretyakov Gallery), 7 minute from metro Tretiyakovskaya. Address in Russian: Лаврушинский переулок 15, Undeground: lines 6 or 8 Tretyakov, stop, line 2  Novokuznetskaya stop.
